{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act16side_level_act16side_08_beg","storyGroup":"act16side","storySort":16,"storyDependence":"act16side_level_act16side_07_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"GA-8","storyName":"影与灰","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"“蕾缪安原谅你，莫斯提马原谅你，伊万杰利斯塔十一世原谅你，就算整个拉特兰都原谅你——我也绝不原谅。”","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act16side/level_act16side_08_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act16side_08","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":14,"next":16,"characters":["教宗","教宗骑士","？？？","艾泽尔","塞茜莉亚","薇尔丽芙","莫斯提马","菲亚梅塔","安多恩"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"dialog","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"character","id":7},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":8,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"subtitle","text":"那是一个伊比利亚的小镇，无论在地图抑或史书，如今你找不到它的名字。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":10},{"type":"subtitle","text":"在还有人生活的时候，那里叫做潮石镇。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":11},{"type":"subtitle","text":"潮石镇的主教抚养了一名年幼的萨科塔。一个萨科塔......在这里成长，在这里学习，度过一生中最美好的岁月。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":12},{"type":"subtitle","text":"这里朴素而贫瘠，但虔诚的生活原本不需要太多。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":13},{"type":"subtitle","text":"只是在大静谧后的伊比利亚，人付出再多努力，生活永远易碎。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":14},{"type":"subtitle","text":"一次瘟疫，一次饥荒，一次早有预谋的渗透，就足以击垮一切。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":15},{"type":"subtitle","text":"为了拯救不是故乡的故乡，萨科塔来到圣城拉特兰，请求一些微不足道的支援。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":16},{"type":"subtitle","text":"他得到的回答很简单：你是我们的一员，他们不是。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":17},{"type":"subtitle","text":"待萨科塔回归伊比利亚，那个“故乡”已然无存。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":18},{"type":"subtitle","text":"甚至一切都被抹去，抚平，仿佛从未存在过。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":19},{"type":"subtitle","text":"像一粒沙消失在沙漠里，一滴水消融于浪潮中。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":20},{"type":"subtitle","text":"萨科塔经历漫长的旅程，又回到拉特兰，形销骨立，宛若游魂。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":21},{"type":"subtitle","text":"他往一座礼拜堂求访获封圣贤的主教，寻求解惑与引导。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":22},{"type":"subtitle","text":"纵是圣贤，面对这许多质疑，也只能沉默。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":23},{"type":"subtitle","text":"他坐在长椅上，坐在那里，从清晨到黄昏。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":24},{"type":"subtitle","text":"菲亚梅塔，那就是我第一次见到安多恩。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":25},{"type":"subtitle","id":26},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":27},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":28},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":29},{"type":"character","id":30},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_bg_26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":31},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":32},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":33},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":34},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$ponder_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_ponder_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":35,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","fadetime":"1","id":36},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"唉。","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#6$1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"算了，自掏腰包吧，这里的维修费用很贵的。","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#6$1","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"下午茶的甜点往后只能减半了。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":43},{"type":"character","id":44},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_358_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"教宗阁下！我听到大教堂方向传来战斗声，您没事吧！","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_358_1#1$1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"这是......？！是异端袭击了您吗？......这是我的失职！","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"别这么紧张，保拉里奥，还记得上次大教堂掰腕比赛的冠军是谁吗？","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_358_1#1$1","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"......是您。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"我只是稍微活动了一下手腕，不小心搞出了一点小意外而已。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"城内的骚乱已经平息了。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_358_1#1$1","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"是的，他们撤退了。我都还没来得及炸爽——","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":61},{"type":"character","id":62},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":63},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"请问可以进来吗？","id":65},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_358_1#1$1","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"咳咳，抱歉，教宗阁下，我失态了。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"我是说，您要找的人已经到了。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"请进吧，孩子们。","id":70,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":71},{"type":"character","id":72},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":73},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":74},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":75},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"教宗阁下，向您致敬......","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#1$1","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"教宗阁下，您好，我是塞茜莉亚。","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/21/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"啊，欢迎，这里有点乱。","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"你们......","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"喝茶一般配什么甜点？","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":86},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":87},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":88},{"type":"character","id":89},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":90},{"type":"dialog","id":91},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_bg_26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":92},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":94,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"您......需要我做什么？","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#8$1","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"嗯，让我想想......","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"往自己的茶杯里加块方糖？","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"艾泽尔，你得多加几块，糖分能舒缓紧张。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"啊！好、好的......","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"教宗阁下，如果我......想要离开拉特兰，您会同意吗？","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ac/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"如果我不允许，你会服从吗？","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"可能不会。","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/94/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"那就去吧。","id":112,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......教宗阁下？","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"我只是个可怜的老头子，最大的愿望就是窝在软乎乎的摇椅里安度晚年，哪有工夫去管小女孩的旅行计划呢？","id":116,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"可塞茜莉亚是......","id":118,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"是什么？难不成她还能是天使和魔鬼的混血，让启示降临的圣徒？","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"塞茜莉亚只是个想要出门看看的小姑娘，对不对？","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"你还带着你妈妈的守护铳，是吗？","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"啊，对不起！我是不是应该交给艾泽尔哥哥......","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#1$1","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"只是......","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/21/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"没关系，孩子。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"获得守护铳是一件庄严的事，原本得举行隆重的仪式，需要监护人出席，导师的首肯，还有一大堆麻烦的文书工作......","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"不过，你也没到可以获得守护铳的年纪。所以，悄悄地把它带走吧。","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"真的可以吗？","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"我不敢说这是给你的礼物。每一把铳都是拉特兰的宝贵财富。","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"不过，若只是孩子思念母亲的寄托，我相信不会有人阻止。","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"带上它吧，孩子。你的身体状况可能不允许你扣下扳机，干掉什么坏蛋......但它能提醒你，不管走到哪里，你都是从拉特兰出发。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......嗯，谢谢您，阁下。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f6/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"艾泽尔，陪着她一起吧，算你的长期外勤任务。","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"记得偶尔回来看看就行。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我......真的有这个资格吗？","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"你当然有。你做出了选择，不是吗？","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......我会竭尽全力。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4036_forcer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"别让塞茜莉亚被欺负了。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"行了，去吧，时光可不等人。到了我这个年纪，就只会满脑子想着睡午觉啦。","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......教宗爷爷。","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f6/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"我会一直走下去的。","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f6/Avg_avg_npc_352_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"......是吗。","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"我将为你祝祷。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":171},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#1$1","id":172},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":173},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":174},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":175},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":176},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":177},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"教宗阁下，这就足够了吗？","id":179,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"我和他们一起吃了点心，这就足够了。","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"......按照您的指示，那个男人已经离开了。","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"我是不是应该多留他一会儿？也许吃块巧克力能让他打起点精神？","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#7$1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"......教宗阁下，您太心软了。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_361_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"不，薇尔丽芙，我们注定无法成为寒夜中的炬火。","id":189,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"但是，为抱薪者端上一杯热茶......总还是做得到的。","id":191,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"“这片大地难以容忍美善”......愿那些不承认这一点的人能够成功。","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"我们也该做下一件事了。骚乱已经平息，召集各国使节吧。","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"启示既昭，我将行我须行。","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":198},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":199},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":200},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":201},{"type":"character","id":202},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":203,"musicid":3},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我经常想起那一夜的事情。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":204},{"type":"subtitle","text":"最初，不过是一个普通的清剿任务，一群普通的萨卡兹劫掠者。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":205},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我们追寻他们留下的逃窜痕迹，找到了那个地方。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":206},{"type":"subtitle","text":"诡异，但没有任何敌意。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":207},{"type":"subtitle","text":"那些......被停滞在自己时间中的残迹。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":208},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我收到了那条临时求援信息......我离开了你们。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":209},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我离开了你们。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":210},{"type":"subtitle","text":"求援的位置很近，来回最多不会超过半天。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":211},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我甚至提前赶回来了......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":212},{"type":"subtitle","id":213},{"type":"dialog","id":214},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"character","id":216},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_26_i16.png","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","x":"-30","id":217},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleTo":"0.8","yScaleTo":"0.8","xTo":"0","duration":"40","block":"false","id":218},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":219},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":220},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我记得脚下砖石的斑驳纹路，我记得冰凉雨水落在脸上的感觉。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":221},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我记得你黑色的角。也记得你紧闭的双眼。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":222},{"type":"subtitle","text":"还有不知所踪的安多恩。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":223},{"type":"subtitle","text":"只是......一次清剿任务而已。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":224},{"type":"subtitle","text":"只是一次清剿任务而已！！！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":225},{"type":"subtitle","text":"为什么事情会落到如此境地？到底哪一步做错了？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":226},{"type":"subtitle","text":"如果我没有离开......如果我留在那里，如果我和你们在一起，是不是这一切就不会发生？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":227},{"type":"subtitle","text":"至少......至少不会......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":228},{"type":"subtitle","text":"至少不是在我赶到的时候，一切都已经注定，什么都无法挽回。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":229},{"type":"subtitle","text":"这感觉糟透了，说真的，糟透了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":230},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我唯一能做的，居然只是看着......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":231},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我本该和你们一起承担。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":232},{"type":"subtitle","id":233},{"type":"dialog","id":234},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"image","id":236},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":237},{"type":"character","id":238},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_bg_26_g10_laterano_roof.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":239},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":240},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$batmeeting_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_batmeeting_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":241,"musicid":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":242},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#1$1","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"别这么想，菲亚梅塔，你不用承担任何东西。","id":244,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"不，这是我的决定。","id":246,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ea/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"我不管他那时正觊觎什么力量，想探究什么秘密，要得到什么答案。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ea/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"我不管他的崇高理想，伟大事业，救赎了谁又引导了谁。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ea/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"我不会原谅。","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"我不为信仰，不为拉特兰城，不为戍卫队，甚至不为逝去的时光......","id":252,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"我不原谅，只因为——","id":254,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"安多恩，你辜负了信任你的人。","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":257},{"type":"character","id":258},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":259},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","fadetime":"1","id":260},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"......是你们。","id":262,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":263},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......为什么你还能安然无恙地出现在这里？！","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"为什么连教宗阁下都......","id":267,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"为什么......","id":269,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"为什么......又有什么为什么......路从一开始就不存在，又能在虚无中寻得什么？","id":270,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#1$1","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"这是你的忏悔？","id":272,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_213_mostma_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"忏悔？不，我没有忏悔......何方可供我忏悔？没有光亮，没有前途，受难者必将受难，悲哀者只有悲哀......","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"没有得救，没有乐园，这里是拉特兰，这里只属于我们......","id":275,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"如果光芒本就是虚影......不，不是虚影......是实在......不如我们所愿......","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"从未有过光芒......又何谈照亮......","id":277,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":278},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你在说什么胡话，安多恩？！","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"......我放弃了吗，我为什么在这里，我放弃了吗？","id":282,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"这障壁如此之厚，我怎么能够拥抱他们？我怎么可以拥抱他们？","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"或许我只是个兜售虚假希望的骗子......骗到自己也信了这说辞......","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"我不明白，我不明白。它的判断是什么？它想让我去向何方？它的存在本身明明已经堵死了我的道路......","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"我向何处寻觅？","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"安多恩！给我清醒一点！看清楚站在你面前的人是谁！","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"是谁......啊......菲亚梅塔......","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你又在发什么疯？！你那副振振有词、理直气壮的样子呢？你的骨头被抽走了吗？！","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"别让我对一个痴人疯汉兴师问罪！看清楚你现在在哪里！","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"......我在拉特兰，菲亚梅塔。我在大教堂之上。","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"很高兴与你们重逢......不，我现在一点也不高兴。","id":297,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":298},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":299},{"type":"dialog","id":300},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bullet_loading","id":301},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":302},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":303},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":304},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":305},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":306},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":307},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":308},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":309},{"type":"dialog","id":310},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":311},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1.7","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":312},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_originiumcast","volume":"1","id":313},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":314},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":315},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"......","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......这不是还会抵挡吗？","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":320},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你还有脸抵挡？！","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"......","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"说对不起。安多恩。","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"现在，跪下来，对莫斯提马，还有蕾缪安的方向，说“对不起”！","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"......","id":330,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你是觉得自己没有错吗？！","id":332,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"我的错误不可胜数。","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你*拉特兰俚语*还挺得意是不是？！","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"不曾。","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_351_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"听着，安多恩，你有什么信念，我不关心，你的信念全完蛋，我也不在意。","id":340,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_300_phenxi_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":341},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":342},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"character","id":344},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_26_i13.png","xScale":"0.9","yScale":"0.9","x":"-40","id":345},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleTo":"0.8","yScaleTo":"0.8","xTo":"0","duration":"60","block":"false","id":346},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":347},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"蕾缪安原谅你，莫斯提马原谅你，伊万杰利斯塔十一世原谅你，就算整个拉特兰都原谅你——我也绝不原谅。","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"......我很抱歉，菲亚梅塔。","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你该道歉的人不是我。","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"......当年的事，若再来一次......也许我仍会这么做。","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......不是吧，认真的？你非要在菲亚梅塔面前这么说？","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"而且你现在不是......","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"很好。安多恩。","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"拿出你的铳。","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"你知道，这不会有结果。","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你以为我*拉特兰俚语*是为了结果？！你以为我在这里把你杀了，蕾缪安的八年就能回来吗？！莫斯提马的人生就能复原吗？！","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"*拉特兰俚语*结果！","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"我要找你算账，是因为我*拉特兰俚语*就是要找你算账！懂了吗？安多恩！","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"......这是你的执念吗，菲亚梅塔？","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"是又怎样？","id":362},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bullet_loading","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"我再说一遍，安多恩——拿出你的铳！","id":364},{"type":"dialog","id":365},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":366},{"type":"dialog","id":367},{"type":"character","id":368},{"type":"image","id":369}],"characters":["教宗","教宗骑士","？？？","艾泽尔","塞茜莉亚","薇尔丽芙","莫斯提马","菲亚梅塔","安多恩"]}